Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.95,0:00:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,颤抖吧  我的右手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.27,0:00:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依照契约  听我号令
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.13,0:00:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缠绕着黑色火焰  满足我的愿望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.46,0:00:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话没办法再热炸鸡了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.84,0:00:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好么  要当实验室成员的话就得和那种人打交道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.30,0:00:28.84,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理  这已经不再是微波炉了  是时间机器了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.94,0:00:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太野蛮了  那么小冈伦买台新的微波炉回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.17,0:00:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没那么多钱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.92,0:00:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过禁止拍我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.08,0:00:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留作纪念…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.52,0:00:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之不要拍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.17,0:00:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  程序搞定了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.01,0:00:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电话微波炉第二版ver  1.03完成
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.10,0:00:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样电话微波炉上的手机就能给想发的号码发送D-Mail了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.73,0:00:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得好  阿至
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.45,0:00:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就再次开始实验吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.00,0:01:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的…是时间机器？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.58,0:01:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不要公开哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.62,0:01:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是店长是不是又会生气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.18,0:01:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工战士
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.56,0:01:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘟嘟噜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.24,0:01:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx85\fscy85}嘟嘟噜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.65,0:01:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理  安静点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.89,0:01:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr.布朗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.19,0:01:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.73,0:01:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爸爸不是Mr.布朗…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.20,0:01:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店长的话外出工作去了  暂时不会回来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.39,0:01:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.18,0:01:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不然我怎么可能在这里偷懒…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.01,0:01:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.29,0:01:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.24,0:01:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.83,0:01:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发光了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.40,0:03:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明多汁炸鸡No.1的话更好吃的说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.19,0:03:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  没买乐倍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.19,0:03:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卖光了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.31,0:03:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是卖光了你就应该去找  直至找到为止
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.85,0:03:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才是作为一个乐倍饭所应该做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.33,0:03:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有就是没有没办法的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.30,0:03:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不喝么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.65,0:03:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.87,0:04:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪个世界会有担心蔬菜摄入量不足的疯狂科学家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.40,0:04:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  开圆桌会议吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.10,0:04:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是把窗户打开吧  不热么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.87,0:04:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么  阿至
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.93,0:04:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是被机关知道了我们的秘密怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.51,0:04:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妄想乙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.61,0:04:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在开始进入掌管过去的女神作战第二阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.61,0:04:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(338,325)\fscy80\fscx80}Operation  Urd
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.23,0:04:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进行让D-Mail更加具有实用价值的实验…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.77,0:04:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天就得喝大麦茶才对呢  萌郁小姐要喝么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.40,0:04:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更有实用价值的话要做什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.52,0:04:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改变过去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.63,0:04:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  那也太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.03,0:04:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是发生时间悖论的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.09,0:04:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,助手啊  你作为一个科学家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.69,0:04:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道就不想试一试能不能用D-Mail改变过去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.91,0:04:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.30,0:04:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是要改变什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.24,0:04:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问得好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.84,0:05:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要通过本次作战来达成的目的  那就是——
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.75,0:05:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,买彩票中奖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.48,0:05:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小冈伦…真由氏表示悲哀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.13,0:05:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我赞成
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.68,0:05:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有钱的话就能买PC的新部件
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.77,0:05:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还可以随便去MayQueen那里玩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.79,0:05:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来  我觉得应该考虑怎样让世界变得更加和平之类的才对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.70,0:05:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如说让世界上每个人都拥有一个呜帕靠枕什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.27,0:05:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈部  你的志向也太低了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.70,0:05:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是确认过去到底能不能改变的实验
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.03,0:05:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是最能够显示出结果的方法么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.21,0:05:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是目的不是钱么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.68,0:05:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴  Celeb17
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.29,0:05:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ce…Cele…  啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.80,0:05:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celeb  17
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.50,0:05:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个花父母的钱住宾馆的人没资格说我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.36,0:05:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经18岁了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.40,0:05:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  彩票不是有很多种嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.39,0:05:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要买哪种的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.72,0:05:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.77,0:05:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.13,0:05:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.34,0:06:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萌郁去哪里了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.42,0:06:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.82,0:06:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  一点都不能大意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.08,0:06:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…你没回信
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.96,0:06:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这难道说就是所谓的「{\1c&0000E0&}sweets（笑）{\r}」？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.08,0:06:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克里斯汀娜  认真看好她别让她随意到处乱跑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.11,0:06:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…就算你让我看好她也…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.99,0:06:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萌郁小姐想看看这间实验室么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.67,0:06:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么过一会我会带你看的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.68,0:06:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是真由氏擅长做的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.36,0:06:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前也带红莉栖看过的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.58,0:06:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先从哪里开始呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.22,0:06:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此  买六合彩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.97,0:06:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每周四公布中奖号码
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.15,0:06:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那个发回过去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.26,0:06:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的要干么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.51,0:06:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有其他更好的提议么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.26,0:06:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要选择哪个号码呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.03,0:07:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便说一下  一等奖…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.66,0:07:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…两亿？！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.21,0:07:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两…两亿？！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.36,0:07:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  阿至
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.78,0:07:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两亿有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.62,0:07:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一…一等奖还是太招人耳目了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.91,0:07:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我还是被机关所追踪的对象
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.02,0:07:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你退缩了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.34,0:07:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二…二等呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.79,0:07:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…两千三百万元
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.37,0:07:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.53,0:07:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七十万
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.48,0:07:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.88,0:07:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈部还真是胆小
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.79,0:07:29.38,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是担心发生时间悖论啊你有意见么Cel-7
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.61,0:07:30.90,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要略成Cel-7啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.89,0:07:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  这就是呜帕靠枕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.36,0:07:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累的时候或者是没精神的时候  就可以抱一抱它
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.72,0:07:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  这个是冰箱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.15,0:07:39.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天里面有…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.38,0:07:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.53,0:07:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  闪光的指压师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.70,0:07:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给你作为实验室成员的第一个任务吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.17,0:07:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是第一件工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.82,0:08:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思考怎样组织D-Mail的短信内容
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.79,0:08:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让一周前什么也不知道的我  去买六合彩的短信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.24,0:08:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七天前的话  也就是168小时…定170秒左右吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.41,0:08:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…  差不多这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.43,0:08:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.98,0:08:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于到了打开命运石之门的时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.74,0:08:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了？  真是不会腻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.41,0:08:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是  不要每次都来泼冷水
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.70,0:08:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为看你们…很开心的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.35,0:08:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没什么好开心的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.54,0:08:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说回来  这位助手还真是一位傲娇小姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.19,0:08:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁是傲娇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.79,0:08:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  牧濑氏懂什么是傲娇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.57,0:08:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.55,0:08:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你那是知道的反应吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.44,0:08:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不知道就是不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.48,0:08:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我就启动微波炉了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.42,0:09:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.06,0:09:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是发生时间悖论的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.58,0:09:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我在担心什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.46,0:09:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,EL  PSY  CONGROO！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.47,0:09:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小冈伦…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.85,0:09:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小冈伦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.97,0:09:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小冈伦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.92,0:10:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.55,0:10:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚…刚才是？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.77,0:10:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在这里站了多久了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.15,0:10:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概30秒左右吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.61,0:10:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,30秒？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.99,0:10:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不记得了么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.75,0:10:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才你不是说要进行用D-Mail改变过去的实验嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.72,0:10:21.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.46,0:10:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然就来到电话微波炉的跟前然后就「哈…哈…」地呻吟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.59,0:10:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由氏  刚才那句「哈…哈…」的再说…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.23,0:10:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴  变态
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.39,0:10:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.43,0:10:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.82,0:10:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈部  你真的没事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.20,0:10:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钱呢？  六合彩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.58,0:10:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cel-7  我中了三等奖了么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.93,0:10:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要叫我Cel-7…  你在说什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.63,0:10:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么…  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.42,0:10:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小冈伦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.79,0:11:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是实验  我们做实验验证是否能够用D-Mail改变过去…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.03,0:11:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说大家现在正在讨论用什么样的内容比较好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.37,0:11:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由氏觉得应该思考怎样让世界变得更加和平之类的比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.14,0:11:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如说让世界上每个人都拥有一个呜帕靠枕什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.21,0:11:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx85\fscy85}真的…不记得了么…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.96,0:11:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.24,0:11:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉佳  欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.11,0:11:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凶真师傅  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.55,0:11:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉佳？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.21,0:11:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.85,0:11:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,02  12  18…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.96,0:11:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.40,0:11:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉佳子  你在哪里知道这个的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.23,0:11:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…  凶真师傅告诉我这个号码的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.20,0:11:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.20,0:11:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说可能会中奖  去买买看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.35,0:11:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.37,0:11:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一周前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.45,0:12:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小冈伦有预知能力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.76,0:12:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么琉佳氏  你中了奖了么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.50,0:12:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个  我搞错了一个号码…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.76,0:12:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可惜  太可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.83,0:12:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈部  你难道用电话微波炉…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.39,0:12:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没买乐倍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.95,0:12:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有就是没有没办法的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.86,0:12:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我确实应该发送了D-Mail
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.85,0:12:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但却没有发信记录
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.34,0:12:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为过去被改写了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.66,0:12:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们记不得实验的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.89,0:12:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明一起商量  一起看着的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.73,0:12:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我还记得
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.26,0:12:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.94,0:13:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种感觉和那时候一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.50,0:13:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.28,0:13:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.66,0:13:17.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是很重要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.72,0:13:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.97,0:13:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一脸好像被洗脑了的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.78,0:13:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗脑…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.68,0:13:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.46,0:13:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被洗脑了的究竟是我  还是他们…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.40,0:13:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.93,0:13:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有被植入芯片
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.34,0:13:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事  没有被洗脑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.28,0:13:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芯…芯片？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.30,0:14:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「洗脑」是指什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.06,0:14:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.56,0:14:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我凤凰院凶真来告诉你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.13,0:14:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绹好像害怕冈部伦太郎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.59,0:14:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有件事想问你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.93,0:14:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放电？  是指那个摇摇晃晃的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.57,0:14:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才有过一次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.39,0:14:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10分钟左右前也应该有过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.53,0:14:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那次没注意到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.97,0:14:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.87,0:14:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.70,0:14:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是个变态啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.60,0:14:36.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不是变态呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.83,0:14:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是「变态绅士」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.67,0:14:41.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样  我说过可以听到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.30,0:14:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到听得这么清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.74,0:14:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说你  连时间机器的事情也…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.57,0:14:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  真行啊  你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.06,0:14:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忠告你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.39,0:14:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  对谁都不会说的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.60,0:14:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说在烦恼着时间机器的事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.26,0:15:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话  问问约翰·提托如何
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.36,0:15:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来提托曾经说过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.14,0:15:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往过去  并改变过去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.11,0:15:12.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(260,325)\fscy80\fscx80}divergence
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.11,0:15:12.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名为世界线变动率的数值会产生变化
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.01,0:15:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界会移动向另一条世界线
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.40,0:15:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在移动时
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.03,0:15:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变化前的世界线的记忆会被消除
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.35,0:15:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在新世界线的记忆会被重新构造
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.63,0:15:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过D-Mail  从琉佳子没买六合彩的世界线
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.02,0:15:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,移动到了买了的世界线
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.05,0:15:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界线发生变化
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.25,0:15:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去的流向也发生了改变
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.02,0:15:43.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是没有把能中六合彩的D-Mail发往过去的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.56,0:15:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是真由理他们不记得了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.69,0:15:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是世界本身就不存在实验这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.33,0:15:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么为何  只有我拥有那个记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.93,0:16:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.17,0:16:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绹  不管被问什么也不能说我偷懒了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.49,0:16:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次能带我坐自行车吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.44,0:16:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带你坐带你坐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.67,0:16:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈部伦太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.08,0:16:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会帮你加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.86,0:16:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.18,0:16:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.45,0:16:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈部  你对我女儿做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.40,0:16:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  我什么也没…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.16,0:16:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴  和我可爱的女儿两人独处
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.32,0:16:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你这样的家伙怎么可能抑制得住欲望
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.40,0:16:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎么看别人的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.21,0:16:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先根本就不是两人独处
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.74,0:16:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到刚才为止铃羽还在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.81,0:16:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.95,0:16:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的吗  绹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.51,0:16:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为说好了  所以不能说她偷懒了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.62,0:16:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.15,0:16:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  打工的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.18,0:16:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢天谢地谢天谢地
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.83,0:16:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙  偷懒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.38,0:16:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,42寸电视怎么一直开着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.85,0:17:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  对不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.53,0:17:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原因之后解释
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.91,0:17:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的实验暂时中止
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.89,0:17:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家就地解散吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.69,0:17:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小冈伦…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.15,0:17:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  那边的助手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.37,0:17:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.31,0:17:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微考虑点事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.00,0:17:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.72,0:17:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回了宾馆也是寂寞的一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.00,0:17:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以希望我搭理你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.15,0:17:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子Cel-7
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.59,0:17:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了别叫Cel-7
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.78,0:17:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要忙着发短信
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.15,0:17:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何都想待在这里的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.37,0:17:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就别碍事  放安静点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.37,0:17:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,325)\fscy80\fscx80\fsp0}The Zombie
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.37,0:17:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复活者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.37,0:17:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个叫法最让人生气
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.54,0:18:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直就像恋爱中的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.70,0:18:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在等喜欢的人发来短信一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.03,0:18:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就那么希望我搭理你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.24,0:18:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发短信的对象是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.98,0:18:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约翰·提托
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.70,0:18:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿至？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.03,0:18:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.16,0:18:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小冈伦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.34,0:18:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我发现了一个不得了的失误
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.59,0:18:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失误？  是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.39,0:18:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际上…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.48,0:18:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把钱包忘在研究所了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.51,0:18:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.27,0:19:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果进不去MayQueen
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.97,0:19:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小冈伦  帮…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.99,0:19:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘟嘟噜  小冈伦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.35,0:19:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  是真由理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.54,0:19:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿至也在一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.46,0:19:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没必要借钱给他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.76,0:19:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.95,0:19:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是小冈伦  打起精神了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.79,0:19:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果还没的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.85,0:19:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱抱真由氏的呜帕也可以的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.91,0:19:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样就能打起精神了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.42,0:19:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我要挂了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.68,0:19:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工好好加油
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.42,0:19:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  再见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.03,0:19:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈部  笑容满面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.85,0:19:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.26,0:19:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看了你的短信
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.29,0:19:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如同你的推测
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.02,0:19:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫无疑问过去改变  世界线进行了移动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.93,0:20:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一不明的地方是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.99,0:20:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还拥有着改变之前的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.31,0:20:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是事实吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.23,0:20:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.70,0:20:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前也发生过同样的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.31,0:20:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.15,0:20:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.65,0:20:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过短信来改变过去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.62,0:20:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我所在的2036年也是未曾预想过的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.37,0:20:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这次改变了过去  移动了世界线
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.26,0:20:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是越过世界线仍保持记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.58,0:20:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能观测到变动的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.24,0:20:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今都未曾确认过
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.24,0:20:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…凶真
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.55,0:20:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你或许拥有那种力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.93,0:20:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是你的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.94,0:20:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许可以引导世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.14,0:20:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往世界线变动率1%的另一边
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.70,0:20:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引导世界？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.42,0:21:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界线变动率1%的另一边是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.59,0:21:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里究竟有着什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.72,0:21:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那前方有着真正的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.62,0:21:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不越过那堵墙壁的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.48,0:21:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来就会成为反乌托邦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.57,0:21:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的目的是改变未来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.71,0:21:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且拥有那力量的或许是你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.90,0:21:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈部…怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.99,0:21:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙在说些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.94,0:21:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将未来…这种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.41,0:22:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凶真  希望你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.34,0:22:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能成为救世主


